Immigration Sales Consultant
Basic Salary: $3000 + Commission + Training Provided
Location: Singapore
Working Hours: 5 days, 9am – 6pm
Job Responsibilities
• Call potential customers through daily assigned leads and secure appointments for the week.
• Provide professional consultation to high net-worth clients.
• Meet up with customers in a sales environment
• Perform sales pitch to interest prospects and close them on the spot.
• Other ad-hoc duties assigned by supervisor and the management
Our Requirements
• Min. 2 years of consultative sales experience
• Min. N Level and above
• Confident and professional
• Excellent interpersonal and negotiation skills
• Immigration experience not required as training will be provided
Singaporean Only
